rows.label: qst106021_msg0001
rows.name:
Welcome back.
Friends collect all materials for
new outfit?

rows.label: qst106021_msg0002
rows.name: Yes, everything we need is right here!

rows.label: qst106021_msg0003
rows.name:
Big sis Kiku! Hana counting on big sis
to make perfect outfit!

rows.label: qst106021_msg0004
rows.name:
Anything for sweet little sister Hana.
Kiku make sure to meet all of requests!

rows.label: qst106021_msg0005
rows.name:
Now Kiku retire to other room to
concentrate on outfit making.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh and, Masterpon was say he have
something to talk to friends about.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0008
rows.name:
It might be a bit soon to hope for
that, Hana-chan...

rows.label: qst106021_msg0009
rows.name:
Masterpon is great inventor, but even
he never finish that quickly.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0010
rows.name:
He say something about getting
Hana herself to make preparations
for upgrade.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0011
rows.name:
Preparations? Like do warm-up
exercise to get body ready?

rows.label: qst106021_msg0013
rows.name:
Hana proud of ability to bend every
joint in any direction!

rows.label: qst106021_msg0014
rows.name:
Is special party trick - er, skill of Hana!
Friends want to see?

rows.label: qst106021_msg0015
rows.name:
No need for that, Kiku think.
Just make sure to talk to Masterpon.
